name: Garden Lace Pocketfold Invitations 25
description:
Lovely vintage botanical's give this pocketfold invitation suite a hint of days gone by. Romance that will always be, and that has always been. Perfect for a spring garden wedding or to make a nod to vintage charms.

Each invitation includes;

-Invitation
-Pocketfold with lace
-Response card or postcard
-Additional enclosure card
-Belly band
-Response postcard envelopes
-Invitation envelopes

UNLIMITED reasonable revisions (Major changes will incur a design fee.
Printed on your choice of uncoated or linen stock.

ORDERS MAY TAKE UP TO 8 WEEKS FOR DESIGN AND PRODUCTIONS.
